### Create a new customer
POST http://localhost:5000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "phone": "123-456-7890",
    "address": "123 Main St"
}

###

### Get all customers
GET http://localhost:5000/api/customers

###

### Get single customer (Replace ID_HERE with a valid MongoDB ObjectId from the GET all customers response)
@customerId = ID_HERE
GET http://localhost:5000/api/customers/{{customerId}}

###

### Create an order for a customer (Replace customerId with a valid ObjectId)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
    "productName": "Wireless Headphones",
    "quantity": 2,
    "price": 150
}

###

### Get all orders
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders
